Summary: Some hacks on planner--muse
Keywords:

* planner-gnus.el: quote planner-gnus-browse-url

* planner-log-edit.el (planner-log-edit-flush-regexp-list): add the possibility to ignore patterns before inserting commit messages as notes (useful for psvn)
(planner-log-edit-add-note): use planner-log-edit-flush-regexp-list

* planner-mhe.el ("mhe"): quote planner-mhe-browse-url

* planner-unix-mail.el (planner-unix-mail-protocol-name): quote planner-unix-mail-protocol-name

* planner.el (planner-annotation-format-local-file-name): add the possibility to format local file links (I use it to force files under my home dir to be displayed as ~/..., so that I can move my planner files easily between home and work)
(planner-annotation-from-file): use planner-annotation-format-local-file-name
(planner-annotation-from-dir): new annotation for handling dired buffers
(planner-annotation-functions): use planner-annotation-from-dir

